productBaseInfoV1.title: Sony PS2 Double Pack
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The PS2 Double pack from Sony will, literally, shock you with its functionality. The accessories in this pack are compatible with the Sony PlayStation 2 console. Ideal for those looking for back-up accompaniments to their gaming experience, this Double pack will be a great buy for those who also need to replace their old accessories. This Double pack from Sony features an 8 MB memory card is exclusively compatible with the PS 2 software. You can store you game progress and scores for easy access, along with special weapons, difficult levels and gamepad or joystick settings in this memory card. The memory card also moves data along faster from one media to another than the older memory cards, taking you faster to your game. So just slip in the 8 MB memory card into your Sony PS2 and always have your favorite games at hand, no matter where you go. The Double Pack also comes with a DUALSHOCK2 analog controller which connects to your console with a wired interface. The DUALSHOCK2 features force feedback for a physical rumble which intimates you of key moments on the screen. This not only increases the realism of the game, it also reduces you reaction time, as you need not rely only on visual cues to stay ahead in the game. The sleek design of the DUALSHOCK2 controller is easy to hold for hours together while you defeat Nazi soldiers in Germany. The button layout is familiar, following the traditional design of most gamepads. The gamepad features pressure sensitivity on every action button, of which there are 4, which let you access combo attacks and other functions inherent in every game. The analog controller also sports increased mobility in the analog thumbsticks, giving you a wider range of movement and control over your on-screen player. This controller also features 2 shoulder buttons and triggers that can be used for additional controls and to launch combination attacks in strategy and FPS games. Both the buttons and triggers are easy to access in the middle of a game, and ensure you always have controls at the tips of your fingers, whether it is to access your arsenal of weapons, or new attack modes. The Sony PS2 Double Pack with a memory card and an analog controller can therefore take your gaming forward to another level of sophistication.

productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Plastic screen protectors are a thing of the past. They do not last, they make scrolling through the screen unpleasant, and writing on the screen with the S-Pen / Stylus leaves a mark. Putting on a plastic screen protector isnt easy either. You have to wipe the phone, spray the screen protector, and use an unreliable squeegee provided to put the difficult piece of plastic on the phone. On top of it all, a plastic screen protector only protects the screen from smudges. Luckily, the Tempered Glass changes all of that. The YourDeal 0.33m Invisible Shield Tempered Glass screen protector is most likely going to protect your screen from a fall more than a phone case. Because the screen protector has a coating over it, dropping the device will more than likely damage the screen protector, not the phone screen itself. The screen is a hair thicker than a plastic screen protector and is much clearer than it as well. To put on the YourDeal Tempered Glass Screen protector, simply remove any phone case and debris from the phone via cloth and adhesive, and then apply the screen shield. The screen attaches on the phone itself and takes little to no time at all to complete. The screen protector is protected for a lifetime, so if the screen ever breaks, simply register online to get a new one and ship it back to the company. Much better than breaking your phone screen and paying for the replacement screen... Right? For the full review of the Glass Screen protector, check out the review below. YourDeal Premium 0.33mm Ultra Thin Tempered Glass are a type of safety glass processed by controlled thermal or chemical treatments to increase its strength compared with normal glass. Tempering puts the outer surfaces into compression and the inner surfaces into tension. productBaseInfoV1.title: Buynow Tempered Glass Guard for Huawei Honor 5X
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Buynow Glass Screen Protector has been specially made with scratch resistant material and rounded edges for a more precise fit. Due to the 0.23-0.33mm thickness and surface hardness of 89H the Glass Screen Protector provides premium protection and no lose in touch screen sensitivity. Surface hardness : 89H : Three times stronger than regular PET film. Even sharp objects such as knives and keys will not scratch the Glass Screen Protector. Oleo phobic Coating : The Glass Screen Protector has an oleo phobic coating that prevents fingerprints and other contaminants and makes the film easy to clean. Anti-Shatter Film : If broken, the Glass Screen Protector cracks into small pieces that are held within the film. They are not sharp, making it safer than other glass products. CAUTION *When removing for re-use, the adhesive properties might wear off to an extent where the screen protector will not adhere to the device. It is not recommended to reuse the Glass Screen Protector once it's been applied. *Using excessive force when installing or removing the screen protector may damage the product

productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Buynow Glass Screen Protector has been specially made with scratch resistant material and rounded edges for a more precise fit. Due to the 0.23-0.33mm thickness and surface hardness of 89H the Glass Screen Protector provides premium protection and no lose in touch screen sensitivity. Surface hardness : 89H : Three times stronger than regular PET film. Even sharp objects such as knives and keys will not scratch the Glass Screen Protector. Oleo phobic Coating : The Glass Screen Protector has an oleo phobic coating that prevents fingerprints and other contaminants and makes the film easy to clean. Anti-Shatter Film : If broken, the Glass Screen Protector cracks into small pieces that are held within the film. They are not sharp, making it safer than other glass products. CAUTION *When removing for re-use, the adhesive properties might wear off to an extent where the screen protector will not adhere to the device. It is not recommended to reuse the Glass Screen Protector once it's been applied. *Using excessive force when installing or removing the screen protector may damage the product

On top of it all, a plastic screen protector only protects the screen from smudges.
